{
  "stem": "21978.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And she was supervised.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "She was not allowed to feed the child with her milk.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "She probably could have had milk.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "She tried sometimes to put her finger into a bowl of soup that she was given for the baby to suck.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "But it didn't help.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "The child was suffering.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "I don't know how long was it, but one nurse obtained-- or was it a doctor, I'm not sure who; I didn't see her, I know only of it-- obtained some syringe and a drug.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "And the mother was given it to inject her own child, kill-- kill it to save it from further suffering.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And the baby, the corpse, was then taken out and thrown out with the other corpses.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "And when Mengele came, he wanted to see the baby.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "And the baby wasn't there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "He was very angry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "I don't know how did it happen that no-- that woman was not punished.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "I don't know what happened then.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "The woman survived.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "She was sent somewhere else.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "But Mengele's experiment was spoiled because he couldn't find out how long unfed baby-- newborn baby-- would live.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "That was one of his experiments.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were just like dogs waiting until he whistles to be taken there and here, to be examined, or do this and that.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was the master of our lives.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We knew that he is holding our lives in his hands.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We could have been sent to work somewhere in Germany.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Maybe we would have survived.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We might have been sent to gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But we were quite young, so we probably wouldn't have, at that time, when we arrived.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But in a way, because selecting us for that special purpose of his, he might have saved our lives.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
